Iranian students are willing to die for their country&#39;s nuclear program.
They formed a human shield.
Several hundred university students formed human shields around nuclear facilities in Iran.
With their gesture they want to express their support for their country&#39;s nuclear program in the face of a possible Israeli attack.
The students began to pray Tuesday at noon outside the facilities and later chanted slogans of death to the United States and Israel.
