Daily menu of an obese child: no breakfast and dinner sausages
More than a third of children between the ages of 9 and 13 are overweight, where overweight affects 9% of the school population and obesity 5%.
Obese children mostly come from families with unhealthy lifestyles, according to current research.
The importance of the environment where one grows for a healthy development of the person is once again demonstrated, as well as the models that serve as reference.
At the table, obsessed children eat, for example, sausages at least twice as often as children from normal-weight families.
For dinner, more than 19% of the obese had eaten fried potatoes the day before the analysis, which is linked to the prevention program &quot;Obesity is not a coincidence&quot;.
In the families of overweight children there is no custom of practicing sports, which is applicable to the majority of today&#39;s families, where only 15% of the children answered that their parents, at least once a week, find time for physical exercise.
Survey conducted on 900 children
The survey was carried out at the end of last school year and almost 900 basic education children from all over the Czech Republic participated in it.
It was already the second edition of the &quot;Obesity is not a coincidence&quot; program, which is supported by the General Health Insurance Company and the Unilever company.
So far, more than 12 thousand children from 4th to 8th grade have participated in the project.
A proper diet and plenty of exercise as a family are determining factors, which significantly reduce the number of overweight and even obese children.
&quot;Only half of the children surveyed have responded that they have five meals a day according to the regime: breakfast, lunch, lunch, snack and dinner, which is one of the basic conditions for a healthy diet&quot;, picks up one of the results of the survey .
Without breakfast but with sausage for dinner
The specialists warn that, in a healthy development, details are also important, which also count, such as having a set time for breakfast as a family.
In the Czech Republic, however, only 23% of school families eat breakfast at the same time.
In most families, everyone eats breakfast alone.
But the worst thing was discovering that in 10% of households they do not eat breakfast at all.
Breakfast is, however, the basis of a correct daily diet.
The study shows that in the families of obese children, unhealthy potato chips are consumed much more frequently.
Almost everyone - regardless of weight - drinks sweet soda every day (70%).
As a general rule, more than 40% of the children surveyed do sports, however, among their parents this result is reduced to less than half, only 15%.
Make your diet
The next phase of the study allowed the chosen kids (204 boys and 172 girls from 13 schools) to create their own diets from all possible offers according to their tastes and opinions.
&quot;The food preferences of Czech children between the ages of 12 and 15, from the point of view of healthy eating, are far from ideal.&quot;
Her favorite foods include pasta, meat, and sweets.
&quot;The popularity of sweet sodas is especially alarming,&quot; warned in the final report of the study.
Pasta takes the cake as the main meal, followed closely by poultry.
Children practically always reject legumes and the taste for fish and vegetables is very low.
Change to healthy habits
At the same time, the study shows that children are willing to change their eating habits if they receive the right information.
&quot;In the control group of study participants, who filled out the questionnaire after finishing the prevention program&quot; Obesity is not a coincidence &quot;, in many cases there was an important change in favor of the principles of a healthy diet &quot;, is pointed out in the results of the study.
It is striking, for example, regarding sweet soft drinks, where many children would begin to prefer normal and running water.
The children would also choose poultry and fish more frequently in the questionnaire for the main meal and would restrict the consumption of sweet foods and those derived from flour.
The stylist must also be a good psychologist, maintain the professionals
In the introductory article, How Stylists Learn, I already complained a bit that the initial lessons were already quite loaded.
I had no idea how this would go.
Conferences by three professionals in the field, how to dress problematic characters and, in addition, a seminar on how it works in show business.
And it will be worse.
The closer the final exams are, the more information and practical tasks await us
And although the course takes place every Saturday and Sunday, there is no longer a pin.
This time we have studied with the director, Alena, (in the course there is no man) on how to dress the woman who does not have a perfect symmetry.
And so is the vast majority.
Someone is short-necked, someone has a slim figure without the proper curves, and someone is overweight.
The stylist must know how to optically soften broad shoulders, lengthen a neck or recreate the necessary curves
They have given us certain tricks on how to make the body of women of the type Jennifer López stand out, with huge breasts and hips but a narrow waist and at the same time not dress her in a too defiant way
If, for example, the difference between the waist and the hips is such that the skirt or pants do not fit, it is worth having at least one extra piece of fabric sewn to measure.
You will certainly not regret it, because the clothes that fit perfectly are priceless.
With a tailored skirt you will feel much better than with one that does not stop moving, getting up, dancing at the waist, etc.
The slim body can be allowed to wear clothes with pleats, embellishments, embroidery or draping.
There are certainly many different types of information and bodies, so I am happy that I have the whole week to put all this information in order in my head.
And even so, I&#39;m afraid that with the assigned task, I already have more than enough.
Each participant in the course has been assigned two celebrities, who will have to design two costumes: one for the day and one for the night.
You have to take into account the current look, the fashion style that suits the person in question.
It was my turn to &quot;dress&quot; Miranda Kerr, perhaps you know her from the Victoria&#39;s Secret campaign.
I scream inside, for me it is much better than, for example, Britney Spears or Christina Aguilera, who lately will have put on a hundred kilos (please, take into account the exaggeration), or the very young Selena Gomez.
The dresses we have to cut them from the magazines or look for them on the internet and print them, and then make them graphically.
The moodboard, which is what the complete result is called, also expresses our personal style and our relationship with graphic design.
It is also important to think about the graphic part of the styling.
The stylist, therefore, does not only dress physically, but also takes care, for example, of product pages in magazines (of specific topics, such as trends, bags, coats, etc.).
The stylist and designer Mario Kameník told us about all this.
But all this is for Sunday.
The stylist must have a global vision.
The three invited specialists animated the conference on Saturday with information on all types of bodies.
Stylist Honza Pokorný, fashion designer Jakub Polanka, and fashion photographer Ben Renč.
Jakub reminded us that fashion is an illusion and the stylist should know how to take advantage of this.
And a good stylist knows how to work with the same garment in different ways.
The variability is, in this case, fundamental.
Thus, such a raincoat (or as they say in English, trench-coat) can be dressed in the classic style with jeans and a T-shirt, but it also serves to dress the naked body with high heels and photograph it as if it were actually a dress.
Or just roll it up and raise your neck to get a totally different image.
&quot;Play with it,&quot; he insisted.
What I value the most is the following advice: &quot;To start working, you first need to know all the rules.&quot;
&quot;Then you can break them,&quot; said Jakub.
At last it is clear to me why we memorize all these formulas, what is combined with what, why, if later it turns out that in fashion magazines we find different results.
Not to mention the parades.
Thanks to photographer Ben, I know that a stylist has to have more types of clothes in stock than he intends to photograph.
Thus, for a fashion story that has ten pages (therefore, ten outfits), at least fifteen must be prepared, ready to use.
And also that the photos the clothes work in combination with other clothes, all of them different from those used in reality.
All this must be taken into account when designing the outfit.
Honza Pokorný assured us that image and style alone are, in many cases, half the success.
Just look at Madonna, who is not exactly an extraordinary singer, but the image and the marketing have made her a world star.
In the Czech Republic, at the moment, there is not yet a clear trend to use the services of stylists.
Even famous people find it useless (my skills are enough for me, my physical appearance is not so important).
And when someone asks us for our services, we must bear in mind that it is very likely that they will indicate a size very different from their real (smaller) size.
Then it only remains to guggle and find out if the gossip magazines have already written on the subject, if a certain celebrity has gained / lost weight, etc.
On Sunday, Honza and Mario insisted that the stylist is not enough to orient himself in fashion, but that he has to understand the outfit.
During your work, above all you must communicate with the people you saw, so it is essential to be a good psychologist.
He knows how to value people, he does not undermine himself, he defends their opinions.
&quot;When a director hires you to classify her wardrobe and complete it with beautiful clothes, you can&#39;t just take and throw away everything that was there and say: &#39;oh what a horror&#39;&quot;.
&quot;Find at least a couple of things that you can weigh and recommend so that someone can put them on,&quot; says Mario.
He himself also showed us that everything must fit into the so-called &quot;placovka&quot;, that is, the job bank.
This is fixed around the waist and all the necessary tools are there.
They are objects such as scissors, such as scissors, lint removers, or safety pins. There is also nylon thread (which is used by the stylist during the photo session of products such as bags or hats), special clips for attaching garments in the front, if it is larger (pins and other types of clips are not allowed, they could damage the fabric), or a sewing kit.
In order not to remain passive listening and put something into practice, we have learned to coat the soles of our shoes.
Even during photo sessions in the studio, on a flat surface, the sole could be damaged and even more so the exterior.
And we did nothing but coat and coat.
We couldn&#39;t touch the shoes with the scissors so as not to accidentally damage them.
So you had to be very clever.
Mario has given me joy by praising my work without reservation.
The truth is that I am not very good at those skills.
This is just a small part of everything we have heard throughout the weekend, in the second part of the course.
I have already realized that dedicating myself to styling at a professional level is not a rosy way, but I do not care exactly what people say.
In Need for Speed: The Run you compete throughout America.
Review
A trip, initially carefree, is complicated by a series of improper carelessness of a routine trip during the morning shift.
To a certain extent, expectations were met, but this is useless, if, in fact, nothing extraordinary was intended to be done.
The new installment, to which The Run is added to the title, aroused great expectations before its premiere.
It promised that it would give new life to the old Need for Speed racing saga and, as a result of what was shown, it appears as a game that should not end up being an action genre without more.
We are also curious to know how the inserted scenes would look, where the main character gets out of the car and walks on his own feet.
As is often the case with NFS series, the results do not vary much from what we expected.
There are races that can be considered acceptable, but in the total count, points are lost due to absurd mistakes, which have been appearing in the series for years.
In reality they cannot even be called errors, but rather it is the incomprehensible reluctance of the programmers.
The adventure begins very well.
You are introduced to a story, whose protagonist, Jack, has certain personal problems; To solve them, he is offered to participate in an illegal race all over America.
You get behind the wheel on the west coast, in San Francisco, and your mission is to get to New York first.
The idea is to offer something interesting.
The route is divided into ten stages and then more than fifty races.
It follows that each race takes place along a different route and the stages are located in different environments, which are quite diverse and interesting.
In this way, one does not even remotely have the feeling that the game always offers the same thing.
Some of the environments are even pleasing to the eye, although the technical level of the graph is equivalent to that of previous installments in the series.
Therefore, it is nothing to write home about.
But the walk through the desert, the autumn landscape or the high mountains covered with snow produce a very pleasant visual effect.
Also, careers are diversified from time to time by an outlier.
Thus, for example, in the desert you find a sandstorm that reduces visibility.
On the other hand, in the mountains you have to be careful not to be buried by an avalanche.
According to that, each of the races is very well developed.
There are only a couple of models, but that is enough.
For a moment, you try to overtake a required number of rivals (the normal in a classic race), then you try to gain time (timed classic duel) and then a duel against a single opponent awaits you.
In the midst of all this, the police sometimes appear, doing nothing but making things even more difficult.
The novelty is the landscapes outside the car.
Interactive animations are presented when Jack, in most cases, has to escape from someone and you have to help him, always pressing the right button at the right moment.
Nothing complicated.
It is surprising, however, that there are far fewer landscapes in the game than you might expect (there are only three in particular).
But the end result is positive, because this element is not annoying and, in the context already mentioned, it is one of the elements that make the game more interesting.
The driving model follows in the footsteps of the previous episodes.
That means that today it is no longer a big thing, but it cannot be said that it is bad.
If you are looking for a realistic simulation, you can already look elsewhere.
But for a race designed with a lot of action, this style of driving is quite suitable, although we can find something better among the games of the competition.
So far, everything in order.
But problems arise after a certain time.
Unlike the correct driving models, the same is no longer true for collisions.
From games of this type it is not expected that it will recreate deformations and complicated collisions, but in fact before a hit against any object, you cannot predict how your car will react, so not everything is in order.
It is typical that, when overtaking very tight or circulating the car with normal traffic, there are only slight frictions, but in other almost identical situations, your car ends up doing uncontrolled pirouettes.
Or even totally destroyed.
Thanks to the reset system, no big problems arise, but it can put you in a bad mood.
The resets are programmed in such a way that, when you have an accident or go off the track, the game restores you to the last rescue point on the track.
However, in each race there are only five available resets.
If you consume all of them, you have to restart the race from the beginning.
So it is only a help in case something does not go well, but it is not very reliable.
Sometimes not even the reset helps, only learning the given stage by heart helps.
A great disadvantage of the game is that the same events are repeated in different places.
In some curves, for example, you have to enter in a specific way; otherwise they are impossible to take.
Other times you find yourself somewhere &quot;civil&quot; vehicles always with the same configuration, even if you are the first, fifth or you arrive five minutes earlier or later.
This makes you mad especially in situations, when you see that two cars that are going to meet in opposite directions, your opponent overtakes without problems, but when you arrive, you must turn or brake.
It is the same when you arrive, because it is programmed because the &quot;surprise&quot; will always happen right under your nose.
The opponents also have one more advantage.
Throughout the game you will reach places where, regardless of the moment, you will always be overtaken by the same opponent in the same place.
Also this happens at the end of the game, on a long bridge, which is even more shocking.
Your opponent must arrive before you, at whatever cost.
When it goes in front of you, it makes it difficult for you to see the cars coming from the front, so at first you can make the car mush.
You can understand the idea of creating a game with maximum doses of suspense and adrenaline, but the execution is so apparent that it will surely disappoint you right away.
And it&#39;s a shame, because although the model of the trip is simple, the game is fun and action-packed, so that often it is not possible to follow in detail what is happening or where.
And it really doesn&#39;t matter, if the idea with fifty exclusive tracks gets the credit or the qualifying in the race so that boredom does not fit, or anything else.
An unusual idea is changing cars during races.
You have to be attentive to the gas pumps on the side of the road, because right there you have to change cars, although in the vast majority of cases what you have will suffice.
Cars are divided into three categories.
Sports cars are suitable for urban areas, strong American cars for straight highways and exotic supercars for technical driving, for example on curvy mountain roads.
In addition, the main narrative thread also appears a parallel challenge thread, that is, there are races in specific places that you will know from the stories.
Here you will get not only medals, but also experience points for your profile, which is useful for both challenges and stories.
Upon reaching the top level, the driver opens up several possibilities, starting with the car and ending with funds for the profile.
At the same time, there is an online Autolog function connected, which compares your results with those of other players and makes other community functions available.
One of the most difficult elements to understand is how the last race in history is made.
With the car you get to the subway tunnel (pass), where you start running in the dark along the tracks (pass).
The speedometer marks you between 150 and 200 km / h (pass) and, suddenly, the metro convoy arrives from behind and takes you straight ahead.
In the newsroom we will surely have a discussion about this for several days, about whether during the programming of the game no one thought even a little or if the authors really take us for a bunch of fools.
The technical part of the game is nothing extraordinary, but at least the general visual effects are in most cases pleasant, sometimes even superb.
Well, what a pity that, in the most tense moments, the image quality is reduced and, sometimes, in a serious way.
This especially affects accidents where many participants are involved, when the continuous image quality is no longer valid.
The audio is fine and the soundtrack is a matter of taste.
In order to appeal to most of the youth group, the soundtrack belongs to the category &quot;each from his father and his mother&quot;, but it can be assumed that no one would buy the game just for its music.
The final feeling of Need for Speed: The Run is therefore quite confusing.
If the game avoided absolutely silly mistakes, we would have trouble claiming that The Run is the best NFS game of recent years.
It gives the feeling that the game is not over.
Fun is guaranteed, but be prepared because mistakes will hit you in the eyes with the force of airport reflectors.
The choirs of the Carolina University will participate in the concert &quot;Students of Velvet&quot;.
The joint celebration of International Student Day and the anniversary of the Velvet Revolution as a musical experience will take place for the third time at the Festa Academica festival.
During it, twenty choirs from secondary and university centers will be presented.
The festival revolves around two concerts on November 17.
&quot;Carolina University has a high participation in the festival.&quot;
Among the current choirs are the choir of the Faculty of Pedagogy and the Faculty of Humanities, in the festival committee is the rector Václav Hampl &quot;, said the head of the organization, Jakub Čaloun.
The highlight of the entire festival is free admission for all audiences to the concert of the secondary choirs, which will be held on March 17 at 2:00 p.m. in front of the National Technical Library in Dejvice.
The program features the participation of the Czech jazz player Karel Růžička and his Celebration Jazz Mass.
