Jürgens also has his own opinion on criticism for the noise of birds: &quot;They are all forms of communication, they have a lot to say.&quot;
The intelligence and skill of these animals are legendary, the rooks not only take advantage of the resources to access schist bites, but also make tools to use them as resources.
